{"tid":1816149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"16歲男被指藏有鎅刀及雷射槍　證據不足獲撒控","createTime":"2020-01-08T04:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T09:43:36.000Z","uid":226984,"like":68,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"cf915ed894c4bc59b5b3c07c8d4a0afa088b684f","tid":1816149,"uid":226984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"大批市民去年 11 月 2 日分別在中環皇后像廣場及遮打花園發起「和理摺紙鶴」及「美國人權法案集氣大會」集會，一名 16 歲男青年被指在集會附近藏有鎅刀及「雷射槍」，遭警方控以一項管有攻擊性武器罪。案件今日( 7 日)在東區裁判法院再度提訊時，控方稱證據不足，申請撤銷控罪，青年當場無罪釋放。<br />\n<br />\n被告王裕豐原被指於去年 11 月 2 日，在中環畢打街與干諾道中交界管有一把鎅刀及「雷射槍」，意圖將其作非法用途使用。控方今日指，經過調查後，基於證據不足，警方與律政司共同決定撤銷控罪，獲裁判官接納，王裕豐當場無罪釋放，他並沒有訟費申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/16%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E9%8E%85%E5%88%80%E5%8F%8A%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E6%A7%8D-%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%92%E6%8E%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F16%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258E%2585%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%2592%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IjrpXFO54mr1mpDNnesGdkc%3D&h=cd670a4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F16%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258E%2585%25E5%2588%2580%25E5%258F%258A%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2593%259A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2592%2592%25E6%258E%25A7%2F&h=d988525b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/16%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E9%8E%85%E5%88%80%E5%8F%8A%E9%9B%B7%E5%B0%84%E6%A7%8D-%E8%AD%89%E6%93%9A%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3%E7%8D%B2%E6%92%92%E6%8E%A7/</a>"},{"pid":"